content: HH The Amir Sheikh Tamim bin Hamad Al Thani held a telephonic conversation with US President Joe Biden on Sunday about the Palestinian issue and ways to end the bloodshed.The two leaders discussed the necessity for an immediate ceasefire, protection of civilians in Gaza and the permanent opening of the Rafah crossing to ensure the flow of relief and humanitarian aid convoys to Palestine.

name: Qatar Living
content: Jamavar Doha unveiled its highly anticipated Winter menu, crafted by Chef Surender Mohan which embodies his profound passion and holistic approach to Indian cuisine. The winter menu promises a delectable journey for diners, with tantalizing appetizers including the savoury Malabar prawns, flavorful Kozhi Roast, and succulent Tandoor dishes like Dakshini Hamour and Tulsi Chicken Tikka. For the main course, patrons can indulge in new selections such as the Kumarakom Sea Bass Curry and Allepey Prawns. To conclude this culinary adventure, Chef Surender presents exquisite desserts, featuring the winter special Shahi Tukda and an irresistible coconut cheesecake.  Saturday to Wednesday from 12:30 p.m. until midnight and Thursday & Friday from 12:30 p.m. until 1 a.m. For reservations:  +974 4485 3000.Jamavar Doha Sheraton Grand Doha Resort & Convention Hotel #Dining #Doha #Qatar #QatarLiving
